name: CHAMBER UNKNOWN
description:
CHAMBER UNKNOWN is a game where you play as a bug, with the goal of destroying the game.

Explore the depths of glitching and bugging your way through levels.

If you get stuck on chamber six, you just have to go in bug mode, and down. Music may be a bit off, thats because its my first time adding music, and also my first time in a jam. Wish i could polish more but i had a lot of homework this weekend.

Made for WowieJam2.
